The '''ventral nuclear group''' is a collection of nuclei on the ventral side of the [[thalamus]]. According to [[Medical Subject Headings|MeSH]], it consists of the following:

* [[ventral anterior nucleus]]
* [[ventral lateral nucleus]]
* [[ventral posterior nucleus]]

